WEBVTT

00:00:00.020 --> 00:00:25.780
Subtitle Provide by dramacool.asia Translator [Admin.@YNG]

00:00:33.820 --> 00:00:35.780
=Lust and Lies=

00:01:03.320 --> 00:01:04.200
You've got guts,

00:01:04.920 --> 00:01:06.239
but you won't live long.

00:01:19.280 --> 00:01:20.079
Protect Governor!

00:01:22.319 --> 00:01:23.640
Capture the person alive!

00:01:23.680 --> 00:01:24.000
Yes, sir.

00:01:24.519 --> 00:01:25.000
Faster!

00:01:42.940 --> 00:01:45.140
=Episode 6=

00:01:56.439 --> 00:01:56.920
Uncle,

00:01:57.840 --> 00:01:58.640
what has happened?

00:02:01.719 --> 00:02:02.719
Did you see Qingwan?

00:02:04.599 --> 00:02:08.080
I saw her rush back to her room.

00:02:27.530 --> 00:02:28.240
Why are you still here?

00:02:28.319 --> 00:02:29.360
Do you want to get caught by Uncle?

00:02:53.680 --> 00:02:54.039
Governor,

00:02:54.319 --> 00:02:54.840
no one is here.

00:02:56.159 --> 00:02:57.080
Bring her back.

00:02:57.680 --> 00:02:58.000
Yes, sir.

00:03:11.879 --> 00:03:13.080
Why aren't you in your room?

00:03:15.319 --> 00:03:15.800
Governor,

00:03:16.680 --> 00:03:17.759
Mother has a headache,

00:03:18.039 --> 00:03:18.960
so I was keeping her company.

00:03:19.520 --> 00:03:21.000
She took Physician Yang's medicine

00:03:21.000 --> 00:03:22.520
and fell asleep, so I left.

00:03:30.319 --> 00:03:31.680
It isn't safe here tonight.

00:03:32.240 --> 00:03:33.319
Go back to your room and rest.

00:03:35.479 --> 00:03:35.960
Yes, sir.

00:03:50.879 --> 00:03:51.639
Keep an eye on her

00:03:52.080 --> 00:03:53.080
these next few days for me.

00:03:53.360 --> 00:03:53.840
Yes, sir.

00:03:54.820 --> 00:03:57.700
(Huo Residence)

00:03:58.240 --> 00:03:59.439
Have the bandits been captured?

00:04:00.039 --> 00:04:00.680
Not yet.

00:04:01.199 --> 00:04:03.560
Governor told me to inform you
not to receive any guests

00:04:04.080 --> 00:04:05.240
for a few days.

00:04:12.919 --> 00:04:13.520
Qingwan,

00:04:13.919 --> 00:04:16.279
this is Sheng Weilian
from the Sheng family.

00:04:16.680 --> 00:04:18.560
You two played together
when you were little.

00:04:18.639 --> 00:04:19.199
Qingwan,

00:04:19.839 --> 00:04:20.480
long time no see.

00:04:27.920 --> 00:04:28.600
Weilian,

00:04:28.879 --> 00:04:29.639
long time no see.

00:04:30.439 --> 00:04:31.000
First Madam,

00:04:31.079 --> 00:04:32.360
your flowers have arrived.

00:04:34.959 --> 00:04:35.480
Qingwan,

00:04:35.920 --> 00:04:37.480
would you like to take a look?

00:05:02.759 --> 00:05:03.399
Looks like

00:05:03.959 --> 00:05:05.360
Mr. Sheng

00:05:05.720 --> 00:05:06.519
has other business here.

00:05:08.480 --> 00:05:09.680
The shipment was raided,

00:05:10.040 --> 00:05:11.480
and we lost heavily.

00:05:11.720 --> 00:05:12.480
But the Huo family

00:05:13.439 --> 00:05:14.639
demands triple compensation.

00:05:15.519 --> 00:05:16.959
That's extortion.

00:05:17.199 --> 00:05:18.680
The cargo was valuable,

00:05:19.240 --> 00:05:20.519
it's worth this price.

00:05:23.515 --> 00:05:24.839
Even though the Huo family

00:05:25.000 --> 00:05:26.199
holds military power

00:05:26.759 --> 00:05:27.560
and controls

00:05:27.560 --> 00:05:28.639
Sucheng,

00:05:29.639 --> 00:05:30.800
the Sheng family

00:05:31.160 --> 00:05:32.800
controls the shipping.

00:05:33.199 --> 00:05:34.800
We're not pushovers.

00:05:44.439 --> 00:05:44.920
Is that so?

00:05:56.160 --> 00:05:56.639
Sit.

00:05:56.879 --> 00:05:57.360
Sure.

00:06:00.560 --> 00:06:01.240
Mother,

00:06:01.480 --> 00:06:02.800
you specially brought me here.

00:06:02.959 --> 00:06:04.079
What is it?

00:06:06.040 --> 00:06:06.680
Qingwan,

00:06:07.639 --> 00:06:10.519
you should spend more time
with Mr. Sheng.

00:06:12.199 --> 00:06:13.160
The assassination

00:06:13.600 --> 00:06:14.639
must've frightened you.

00:06:20.199 --> 00:06:20.959
There are things

00:06:21.480 --> 00:06:22.560
I must tell you.

00:06:23.800 --> 00:06:25.240
What the Huo family has today

00:06:25.639 --> 00:06:27.800
was built on countless lives.

00:06:28.240 --> 00:06:29.279
All this while,

00:06:29.560 --> 00:06:32.160
many have wished
the Huo family destroyed.

00:06:32.480 --> 00:06:33.279
I hope

00:06:33.439 --> 00:06:35.120
the Sheng family can protect you.

00:06:36.480 --> 00:06:37.839
Mother, do you mean

00:06:38.360 --> 00:06:40.000
you want me to marry Sheng Weilian?

00:06:41.279 --> 00:06:43.120
The Sheng family is the best choice.

00:06:45.639 --> 00:06:47.000
Jin and you are innocent.

00:06:47.800 --> 00:06:48.720
As a mother,

00:06:49.319 --> 00:06:51.040
I must prepare a backup for you.

00:06:53.319 --> 00:06:54.079
Mother,

00:06:55.279 --> 00:06:56.639
what about you?

00:06:58.199 --> 00:06:59.160
Me?

00:07:00.199 --> 00:07:01.839
As the matron,

00:07:02.879 --> 00:07:04.160
I should share

00:07:05.680 --> 00:07:07.480
the guilt.

00:07:16.639 --> 00:07:17.120
Aunt,

00:07:17.639 --> 00:07:18.959
I've made you white fungus soup.

00:07:19.120 --> 00:07:20.040
Please have some.

00:07:24.319 --> 00:07:24.920
Qingwan,

00:07:25.160 --> 00:07:26.680
go keep Mr. Sheng company.

00:07:36.079 --> 00:07:36.600
Aunt,

00:07:37.399 --> 00:07:38.480
I spent the whole day

00:07:38.519 --> 00:07:39.639
making this.

00:07:39.879 --> 00:07:40.600
People say

00:07:40.720 --> 00:07:42.120
it's good for the skin

00:07:42.120 --> 00:07:43.120
and health.

00:07:43.319 --> 00:07:43.920
Try some.

00:07:43.959 --> 00:07:44.720
You're so thoughtful.

00:07:49.959 --> 00:07:51.240
If you wish to negotiate,

00:07:51.759 --> 00:07:53.360
at least show sincerity

00:07:54.160 --> 00:07:56.000
instead of harsh words.

00:08:00.000 --> 00:08:00.519
Please leave.

00:08:06.279 --> 00:08:07.120
Weilian,

00:08:07.360 --> 00:08:08.920
why not go first?

00:08:11.160 --> 00:08:11.920
You just came.

00:08:13.120 --> 00:08:14.240
How could I leave so soon?

00:08:21.839 --> 00:08:23.279
Don't treat just any man like a brother.

00:08:26.120 --> 00:08:26.720
True.

00:08:27.240 --> 00:08:27.920
After all,

00:08:28.279 --> 00:08:29.439
your real brother

00:08:29.720 --> 00:08:30.759
is Young Marshal Huo.

00:08:31.040 --> 00:08:31.720
If

00:08:32.360 --> 00:08:33.639
we were to marry,

00:08:34.919 --> 00:08:36.440
that wouldn't be proper.

00:08:41.600 --> 00:08:43.840
If you still want your hand,

00:08:45.519 --> 00:08:47.080
move it away.

00:09:03.039 --> 00:09:03.680
Go back to your room.

00:09:06.080 --> 00:09:07.320
I'm not your soldier.

00:09:07.799 --> 00:09:09.120
Why should I take orders from you?

00:09:13.720 --> 00:09:14.600
You're my sister.

00:09:15.759 --> 00:09:17.039
I have a duty to keep you safe.

00:09:17.960 --> 00:09:20.480
Stay away from scoundrels
who flirt around.

00:09:21.039 --> 00:09:23.559
Someone as ruthless as you

00:09:25.000 --> 00:09:26.639
is hardly in a position to judge me, no?

00:09:27.159 --> 00:09:28.480
Miss Huo, here's the thing you asked for.

00:09:34.000 --> 00:09:35.600
The temple fair is in a few days.

00:09:36.120 --> 00:09:37.120
Anyone wants to go?

00:09:37.480 --> 00:09:38.240
I remember

00:09:38.679 --> 00:09:39.519
Young Marshal Huo

00:09:40.320 --> 00:09:42.600
must keep order in Sucheng
on those days.

00:09:42.919 --> 00:09:44.000
He probably won't make it.

00:09:44.519 --> 00:09:45.960
If so, I'll trouble you

00:09:46.080 --> 00:09:46.960
to pick me up that day.

00:09:47.960 --> 00:09:48.320
Sure.

00:10:28.900 --> 00:10:34.300
♪Listen, the bell rings from afar♪

00:10:35.340 --> 00:10:41.380
♪The fog lifts, your image still hazy♪

00:10:41.860 --> 00:10:48.020
♪Do you remember the sound of the flute
in the wind?♪

00:10:49.540 --> 00:10:54.980
♪It whispers of the flame we shared♪

00:10:59.700 --> 00:11:06.140
♪Having seen those prophecies
left behind♪

00:11:06.140 --> 00:11:09.980
♪A sudden will to survive arises♪

00:11:09.980 --> 00:11:13.580
♪The ruan resounds with grandeur♪

00:11:13.580 --> 00:11:16.980
♪Under the pelting plum rain♪

00:11:16.980 --> 00:11:20.260
♪Everyone sings the final act♪

00:11:20.260 --> 00:11:24.460
♪All fading away♪

00:11:26.860 --> 00:11:30.980
♪The curtain falls♪